    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and totally ready for its next adventure! It runs smoothly, looks sharp, and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home. It's a perfect blend of comfort and performance. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and tell you more!",
