    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure internal longevity. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates, mitigating the common fatigue points of this platform. Suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and a limited-slip differential that provides exceptional mechanical grip through the apex. Finished in a classic colorway, the interior displays light patina on the Nappa leather bolsters, consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle. A technically sound driver's car for those who prioritize analog feedback and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
