    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in solid overall condition, offering a perfect balance of performance and practicality. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal the minor stone chips and light surface marks typical of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the upholstery shows only minimal wear on the bolsters, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. The engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts smoothly, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It is a dependable, honest machine that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence and peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
