    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of it, and it's ready for a new home. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without breaking the bank. Come take it for a spin, you'll love how it handles!",
      "price": 28900.0,
