      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. This specimen excels mechanically, boasting individual throttle bodies and a variable M differential lock that ensures precise power delivery to the rear wheels. Recent service includes documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator updates, addressing the platform's primary tactile concerns. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates, while the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering offers feedback missing from modern EPS systems. A true purist's configuration optimized for high-induction performance.",
